{"tid":2373205,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"嫌托運費貴！4男機場「吃完60斤橘子」崩潰：再也不吃了","createTime":"2021-01-20T09:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T09:49:04.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ffa583c80afb4b28858f0f3c1d1bbf6e54b6be1","tid":2373205,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／黃韻璇報導<br />\n<br />\n搭飛機如果行李超重就要付額外費用，若是出國的話有很多東西是不能帶上飛機的，近日在中國就有4名男子出差時買了60斤的橘子，雖然幾人搭的是中國的國內線，可以攜帶水果，但是因為覺得託運費太貴，竟然在機場吃完所有橘子，幾個人崩潰直說「再也不想吃了」。<br />\n<br />\n據《北晚新視覺》報導，這起事件發生在中國雲南昆明，1月14日王先生和3名同事出差，準備搭飛機回家前，幾個人買了一箱橘子當伴手禮，花了50元人民幣（約216元新台幣），然而到了機場才發現，這箱60斤重的橘子要額外付託運費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/20/2992979-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2F2992979-PH.jpg&h=4f4cb13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n託運費用高達300元人民幣（約1300元新台幣），光是託運費用已經可以買6箱橘子，讓4名男子覺得相當不划算，討論後決定不託運，然而橘子都買了不能浪費，幾個人居然站在機場30分鐘，吃完整整60斤橘子，崩潰表示「再也不想吃橘子了」，且因為吃太多橘子上火，王先生表示「3天後我們4個人的嘴角都起水泡」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=885134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D885134&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1IaxVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=32dc6d32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D885134&h=921688c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=885134</a>"},{"pid":"81d1f9824df78d255287eb5c4b7f073e9c2e6741","tid":2373205,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:32:10.000Z","msg":"自私到分啲比人食都唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0e48f60be906a7cd6144ae78ef2ef06a29bd47","tid":2373205,"uid":128705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"81d1f9824df78d255287eb5c4b7f073e9c2e6741","tid":2373205,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:32:10.000Z","msg":"自私到分啲比人食都唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"現場賤賣都有人買掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲支那人成日食到自己收皮咁戇鳩"}]}